00:35:28.604 --> 00:35:30.525
mula sa dalawang alagad upang buhayin ang mga bagay?

00:35:40.485 --> 00:35:41.485
Wu Bei,

00:35:41.684 --> 00:35:43.840
tinatawag kang tanga

00:35:44.365 --> 00:35:46.496
mapapahiya ang termino mismo.

00:35:47.084 --> 00:35:49.405
Papalapit na ang Ascension Array.

00:35:49.485 --> 00:35:51.040
Kailangan natin ng espirituwal na enerhiya ngayon.

00:35:52.084 --> 00:35:53.045
pa ikaw

00:35:53.084 --> 00:35:55.164
paulit-ulit itong sayangin

00:35:55.244 --> 00:35:56.480
sa mga personal na sama ng loob.

00:35:57.045 --> 00:35:58.688
Talagang katangahan!

00:35:59.525 --> 00:36:00.485
aking panginoon,

00:36:02.445 --> 00:36:04.204
Nais ko lamang magdagdag ng ilang kasiyahan.

00:36:04.845 --> 00:36:06.485
Ang Soberano ay matalinong nagsasalita.

00:36:07.005 --> 00:36:08.124
