Ang Soul Anchoring Lamp ay hindi karaniwan.

00:36:51.284 --> 00:36:52.525
Saan mo ito nakuha?

00:36:52.764 --> 00:36:54.045
Ano ang layunin mo dito?

00:36:54.204 --> 00:36:55.204
Bakit ang daming tanong?

00:36:55.204 --> 00:36:55.925
