00:37:26.764 --> 00:37:28.005
ang kanyang maitim na cultivator na dugo.

00:37:32.005 --> 00:37:33.204
Ang Kong Hou ay lampas sa kaligtasan.

00:37:33.325 --> 00:37:34.805
Siya ay isang ipinanganak na dark cultivator.

00:37:35.405 --> 00:37:36.445
Soul Anchoring Lamp

00:37:36.925 --> 00:37:37.885
